&lt;County Ltd>, which is acting in concertwith Tesco Plc &lt;TSCO.L> in its 151.4 mln stg for supermarketchain operator &lt;Hillards Plc>, has purchased 300,000 Hillardsordinary shares at 316p per share, a statement said.    These purchases, together with those made by County on 10March, represent about 4.8 pct of Hillards issued ordinaryshare capital, it said.    Tesco's offer, made on March 10, values each Hillardsordinary share at 305.5p, a 37.6 pct premium over the previousday's  closing price. A cash alternative of 290.55p will bemade available. REUTER&#3;